<td>Use generic text ("click here")</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Link to genuinely helpful resources (even if not yours)</td>
<td>Only link to your own content</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Limit to 1 link per answer</td>
<td>Include 3+ links per answer</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
